    <item>
      <title>卡尼（Carney）招募了前金牌银行家霍奇森</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/carney-recruits-ex-goldman-banker-hodgson-for-political-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）招募了前高盛银行家蒂莫西·霍奇森（Timothy Hodgson），他曾是加拿大银行的顾问，在该国当选中竞选自由党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/carney-recruits-ex-goldman-banker-hodgson-for-political-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 02:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署针对律师事务所詹纳（Jenner）和布洛克（Block）的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-signs-executive-order-targeting-law-firm-jenner-and-block</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项行政命令，针对詹纳（Jenner）的律师事务所，并在该公司的一名前合伙人中担任了一名特殊顾问罗伯特·穆勒（Robert Mueller）的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-signs-executive-order-targeting-law-firm-jenner-and-block</guid>
